comments: Siakam (TOR) engages with Tillman (MEM) off-ball and marginal contact occurs as Siakam (TOR) releases away to retrieve the pass.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) is in the paint for at or about three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Aldama (MEM) contests Siakam's (TOR) jump shot and marginal contact occurs to his forearm after the completion of his follow-through.
Siakam (TOR) briefly places his hand to Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) side while defending his drive to the basket.
Achiuwa (TOR) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) body while retreating during the drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Barnes (TOR) initiates contact with Tillman's (MEM) wrist, which affects his play at the basket.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) briefly places his hand to Achiuwa's (TOR) shoulder and removes it as they elevate to the rim height to pursue the loose ball.
Tillman (MEM) establishes himself in Trent Jr.'s (TOR) path and makes marginal contact to Trent Jr.'s side as he rolls to the basket.
Aldama (MEM) is moving alongside Barnes' (TOR) path and marginal body contact occurs during Barnes's (TOR) drive.
Siakam (TOR) and Tillman (MEM) come together in the lane and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the loose ball.
VanVleet (TOR) establishes himself in Aldama's (MEM) path and slightly extends his arm against Aldama as he defends over the screen.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) is moving alongside Barnes's (TOR) path and marginal body contact occurs during the drive.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) places a resting hand to Barnes' (TOR) front during his upward shooting motion, and marginal body contact occurs during his shot attempt at the basket.
Bane (MEM) establishes himself in Barnes's (TOR) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Green (MEM) continues to re-establish himself following the initial contact and further restrict VanVleet's (TOR) ability to defend over the screen.

Replay review of the foul called on VanVleet (TOR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. VanVleet (TOR) makes contact with the ball during Banes' (MEM) shooting motion and dislodges the ball away before incidental arm contact occurs.
Konchar (MEM) and Trent Jr. (TOR) engage in marginal contact with one another during the entry pass.
Bane (MEM) places his forearm to Trent Jr.'s (TOR) front and immediately slides his hand off at the start of Trent Jr.'s drive.
Konchar (MEM) commits a take foul on Trent Jr. (TOR). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Konchar (MEM) briefly places his hands against Trent's (TOR) body as he gathers the entry pass and marginal contact occurs as he releases his pass attempt.
Tillman (MEM) commits a take foul on Siakam (TOR). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes more than two steps before releasing his jump shot attempt.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) engages with Barnes (TOR) off-ball and marginal contact occurs as Jackson Jr. (MEM) releases away to retrieve the pass.
Barnes (TOR) legally contests Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Siakam (TOR) places his hand to Aldama's (MEM) side in the lane and slides his hand off as they pursue the loose ball.
